reviewText: Pretty bad. SO bad, that I turned it off. Don't waste your money- bollywood has much better films out there- for the whole family to enjoy- this was NOT good.
This movie is a great one to sit down with the family and have a good belly laugh. The comical adventure had my daughter laughing but unable to turn away. It was great fun for the whole family.

This is a cute Hindi film. The kids seemed to enjoy it. I would rate it along with cheap made-for-kids Hollywood cartoons. It's not Disney or Pixar - just a ride through a kid's imagination, just for fun.
